  "instructions": [
    "Heat coconut oil in a large Dutch oven over medium heat.",
    "Add the onion and sauté until translucent, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the Thai red curry paste and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the daikon and cook for 5 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Pour in the coconut milk, maple syrup, apple cider vinegar, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Bring to a simmer and cook, covered, for 20 minutes.",
    "Stir in the toasted coconut flakes and fresh cilantro.",
    "Serve warm, garnished with additional cilantro if desired."
